# artificial-jellybeans

A Claude Code marketplace for jellybeans.

See the [manifest](./.claude-plugin/marketplace.json) for list of included plugins.

## Installation

Add the marketplace to Claude Code:

```bash
/plugin marketplace add thesimonho/artificial-jellybeans
```
